

## To see list of saved connections, use (<SavedWiFiConn>)

$ nmcli c

## To see list of available WiFi hotspots (<WiFiSSID>)

$ nmcli d wifi list

or 

$ sudo iwlist wlan0 scanning

## To see list of interfaces (<WifiInterface>)

$ ifconfig -a

====================================================

## To connect one of list of wifis

$ nmcli d connect (<WifiInterface>)

or

$ nmcli c up <SaveWiFiConn>

## To disconnect one of list of wifis

$ nmcli d disconnect (<WifiInterface>)

or

$ nmcli c down <SaveWiFiConn>


## GUI interface 

$ nmtui
